      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DT"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-dat                to   w-tot-dat-att          .
       pre-exe-pgm-999.
           exit.

