           add       w-tot-ord-tiv        to   w-tot-fnt-tiv          .
           add       w-tot-ord-tot        to   w-tot-fnt-tot          .
           if        w-tot-ord-vpf        not  = w-tot-fnt-vpf
                     move  spaces         to   w-tot-fnt-vpf          .
