      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da stampare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tot-ord-tot        =    zero
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-999.
           if        w-tot-ord-nrg        not  > 1   and
                     w-tot-ord-vpf        =    c-sgl
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-999.
       prn-fin-lr1-050.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se righe residue sufficienti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-res                >    2
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-100.
