           perform   prn-liv-det-agt-000  thru prn-liv-det-agt-999    .
       prn-liv-det-040.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento numero righe ordine               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tot-ord-nrg        <    99999
                     add   1              to   w-tot-ord-nrg          .
       prn-liv-det-060.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa riga di dettaglio                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
