           if        srt-umi-prz          =    spaces
                     go to prn-liv-det-999.
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      128                  to   p-pos                  .
